        "summaries": {
          "bn": "ইমাম জাফর আস-সাদিক (আ.) গীবত সম্পর্কে ফিকহি নীতি প্রতিষ্ঠা করেছেন।",
          "de": "Imam Ja'far al-Sadiq (Friede sei mit ihm) legt ein rechtliches Prinzip zur üblen Nachrede (Ghiba) fest.",
          "en": "Imam Ja'far al-Sadiq (peace be upon him) establishes a jurisprudential principle regarding backbiting (ghiba): when a person openly and shamelessly displays sinful behavior, the prohibition of backbiting does not apply to them. In Islamic ethics, backbiting is normally a grave sin (cf. Quran 49:12), but this hadith carves out an exception for those who publicly flaunt their transgressions, as they have forfeited the right to reputation protection by their own open conduct.",
          "es": "El Imam Ja'far al-Sadiq (la paz sea con él) establece un principio jurisprudencial sobre la murmuracíon (ghiba).",
          "fa": "امام جعفر صادق (علیه السلام) اصل فقهی درباره غیبت بیان فرمودند: کسی که آشکارا گناه می‌کند، غیبت او حرام نیست.",
          "fr": "L'Imam Ja'far al-Sadiq (établit un principe juridique concernant la médisance (ghîba).",
